      "content": "everything is just getting so much harder lately. my joints ache every single day and i can barely even walk to the mailbox without needing to sit down. it feels like my body is just a cage that's slowly closing in on me. i'm just sitting here in this quiet house and it feels like i'm already gone, you know? just waiting for the clock to run out.",
