      "content": "The struggle with pain and the feeling of being a burden is so heavy, and it makes perfect sense that you feel like those quick fixes aren't enough. Your worth isn't tied to your ability to move or be independent; you are a person who deserves to be cared for. If you feel like you have nothing left to give, please know that there are people who want to listen to the depth of your pain without judgment. Connecting with a crisis line can offer a safe space to talk about these overwhelming feelings right now.",
